on thursday june 12 2003 the times published an editors note stating that ten additional articles by jayson blair who resigned on may 1 as a reporter were found to include misrepresentations or possible borrowed passages an accounting of those articles was published online at nytimescom correctionshtml this article was among those described the description 'chief in sniper case considers a job change mr blair wrote that charles a moose the police chief in montgomery county md served in the air national guard at langley air force base in virginia he served at andrews air force base in maryland the same error appeared in an article by mr blair on march 21 2003

